---
// Slide2
---
<section class="slide-container">
      <span class="slide-number">02 / 16</span>
      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i> Обо мне</h2>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-header">
          <img class="about-logo" src="logo.jpeg" alt="MicroStudio logo">
          <div class="about-header-content">
            <h3>Основатель digital-агентства <strong>MicroStudio</strong></h3>
            <p class="tagline">Создаю цифровые продукты, которые приносят результат</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="about-list">
          <li>
            <span class="about-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i></span>
            <span>Создание сайтов и приложений</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="about-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-gears"></i></span>
            <span>Скрипты оптимизации бизнес-процессов и логики</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="about-icon green"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></span>
            <span>Интеграция ИИ в бизнес</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="about-icon gold"><i class="fa-solid fa-money-bill-trend-up"></i></span>
            <span>В общем — всё, что приносит деньги сейчас 💰</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="about-experience">
          <img class="melbet-logo" src="melbet.png" alt="MelBet logo">
          <div class="experience-text">
            <h4>Прежде чем основать MicroStudio</h4>
            <p>Я работал разработчиком в компании MelBet — получил опыт в крупной IT-компании и понял, что хочу своё
              дело</p>
            <span class="role-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> Разработчик</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/microstudio_official/" target="_blank" class="about-link instagram">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i> Инстаграм компании
          </a>
          <a href="https://microstudio-official.vercel.app" target="_blank" class="about-link website">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> Сайт компании
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

<style is:global>
/* Slide 2 — About me */
.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  flex: 1;
  align-items: center;
}

.about-header {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
  gap: 28px;
  align-items: center;
}

.about-logo {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
}

.about-header-content h3 {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1e293b;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.about-header-content .tagline {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #64748b;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.about-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px 40px;
}

.about-list li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #1e293b;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.about-list li .about-icon {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  min-width: 36px;
  background: #eff6ff;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.about-list li .about-icon i {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #2563eb;
}

.about-list li .about-icon.green {
  background: #f0fdf4;
}

.about-list li .about-icon.green i {
  color: #16a34a;
}

.about-list li .about-icon.gold {
  background: #fefce8;
}

.about-list li .about-icon.gold i {
  color: #d97706;
}

.about-experience {
  background: #fefce8;
  border: 2px solid #fde68a;
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 20px 28px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
}

.melbet-logo {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  min-width: 80px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  object-fit: contain;
  background: #ffffff;
  padding: 6px;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}

.experience-text h4 {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1e293b;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.experience-text p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #64748b;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.experience-text .role-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #fde68a;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 4px 14px;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: #d97706;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.about-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.about-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: #f8fafc;
  border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 12px 22px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1e293b;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}

.about-link:hover {
  background: #eff6ff;
  border-color: #bfdbfe;
  color: #2563eb;
}

.about-link i {
  font-size: 20px;
}

.about-link.instagram i {
  color: #e1306c;
}

.about-link.website i {
  color: #2563eb;
}

/* Slide 2 — Intro */
.intro-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
  flex: 1;
  align-items: center;
}

.question-card {
  background: #f8fafc;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 32px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}

.question-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
}

.question-card .q-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  background: #eff6ff;
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.question-card .q-icon i {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #2563eb;
}

.question-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1e293b;
}

.question-card p {
  color: #64748b;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.intro-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 340px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}
</style>
